{"tid":170538,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經營日式風俗店請非法女外勞接客　4男女被捕","createTime":"2017-03-24T18:03:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T01:20:01.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe6dc8addd796b15e058d367c105381b4435f50","tid":170538,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T18:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2414/d2414295.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2414%2Fd2414295.jpg&h=e170be95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">▲在日本經營風俗店不算違法，但聘用非法外勞則是犯罪行為。（圖／翻攝自網路）</span><br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n4名中國籍男女在日本東京開設日式風俗店，同時招聘無工作證的華裔女子及留學生賣淫。4人被當地警方以涉嫌違反入境管制法中的教唆非法就業罪名，周五日連同其他3名中國籍男女一同拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n被捕的4名男女包括38歲的負責人孫偉偉，擔任按摩女的21歲女留學生王婷，以及兩名分別負責駕車接送女子知恩客的28及30歲中國男子。4人已承認控罪。<br />\n<br />\n案情指出，涉案的網上風俗店以中國遊客及在日墨西哥裔外勞為對象，並以性工作者能說中、英、日三國語言作招徠。聘用的女子主要是持旅客簽證入境的中國人，當中也有留學生，但全都沒有工作許可證。<br />\n<br />\n該店自2008年1月開始經營，直到今年2月營業額已逾5億日圓(約1.3億台幣)。在日本經營風俗店不算違法，但聘用非法外勞則是犯罪行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170324/891378.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170324%2F891378.htm&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=78172dd6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170324/891378.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a982a54b21584905a728ad9be1afa33b3c5673b3","tid":170538,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T18:13:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606802188260f80cedd4fce420cfbeb071129e16","tid":170538,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T18:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5069edc6a28946d8321a12082e4feb768117253","tid":170538,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T19:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353a5ebfbde29e059cf7f5650ca27c0841d559b6","tid":170538,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T20:07:44.000Z","msg":"假雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d18c4d66beffa3ae6d65a35a50a6c1e58178a0","tid":170538,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T20:29:15.000Z","msg":"係d嫖客報串都唔奇<br />\n特登去日本就係為左食日本菜，屌你老味竟然塞碟宮保雞丁黎<br />\n比著係我一定發火"},{"pid":"42bff0f4bf9508f63ffaf36f9c3cbc488e7eec85","tid":170538,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T01:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}